data.description: Come check out this charming bungalow at 2694 Chrysler, set on a spacious 'double lot.' The appeal of this property is enhanced by its unique lot size, offering extra space for various possibilities. With a double lot, fenced backyard, and spacious garage, this property offers versatile outdoor spaces. Whether you envision a garden oasis, outdoor gatherings, or a play area for children, the options are limitless. Enjoy the freedom and security of the fenced-in backyard, providing an ideal space for pets to roam and play. Whether you have furry friends or simply value the privacy, this feature adds to the overall appeal of the property. A recent addition to this property is a brand new roof, offering not only aesthetic appeal but also ensuring added durability and peace of mind for the future. The detached garage offers ample space for both cars and storage, providing a practical solution for your parking and organizational needs. Make the most of this bonus space for vehicles, tools, or hobbies.  More photos to come!
